Package: nbTransmission
Title: Naive Bayes Transmission Analysis
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2019-09-06
Authors@R: person("Sarah V", "Leavitt", email = "sv1205@bu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Sarah V Leavitt <sv1205@bu.edu>
Description: A package containing functions to calculate relative transmission
    probabilities using naive Bayes and use these probabilities to estimate
    transmission paramaters such as the serial interval and reproductive number.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Encoding: UTF-8
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/sv1205/nbTransmission 
BugReports: https://github.com/sv1205/nbTransmission/issues
